  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "Minimal-profile UnitOfAssurance for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. Thirteen credibility factors are assessed under ASME V&V 40-2018. No context of use is bound to this package; intended-use scope is therefore undefined. Decision: Accepted.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5",
